Algorithm :
Algorithm: Integrated Knowledge-Based Question Answering
1)Start
2)Convert input text into structured representation
3)Load world knowledge and scripts
4)Store both text facts and world knowledge
5)Accept question from user
6)Convert question into structured form
7)Match question with text facts
8)If answer not directly found, apply inference using world knowledge
9)Generate inferred answer
10)Display answer
11)Stop

Flowchart:
 ┌───────────┐
 │   Start   │
 └─────┬─────┘
       │
 ┌─────▼──────────────────┐
 │ Convert Text to         │
 │ Structured Form         │
 └─────┬──────────────────┘
       │
 ┌─────▼──────────────────┐
 │ Load World Knowledge &  │
 │ Scripts                 │
 └─────┬──────────────────┘
       │
 ┌─────▼────────────┐
 │ Input Question   │
 └─────┬────────────┘
       │
 ┌─────▼──────────────────┐
 │ Direct Answer Found ?   │
 └─────┬─────┬────────────┘
       │Yes  │No
       │     │
 ┌─────▼───┐ ┌───────────────┐
 │ Return  │ │ Apply          │
 │ Answer  │ │ Inference      │
 └─────┬───┘ └─────┬─────────┘
       │           │
       └─────┬─────┘
             │
       ┌─────▼─────┐
       │ Display   │
       │ Answer    │
       └─────┬─────┘
             │
       ┌─────▼─────┐
       │   Stop    │
       └───────────┘
